@startuml
actor Administrator
boundary View
control ReportController
entity DataModel
database Database

Administrator -> View: Akses Halaman Rekap Platform
alt Terapkan Filter Waktu/Status?
    Administrator -> View: Input Filter & Terapkan
    View -> ReportController: GET /report?start=...&end=...
else Tanpa Filter Khusus
    View -> ReportController: GET /report
end

ReportController -> DataModel: query data(filters)
DataModel -> Database: SELECT aggregations
Database --> DataModel: Result Set
DataModel --> ReportController: Collection Data

alt Pilih Export? (Cetak PDF)
    Administrator -> View: Klik Export PDF
    View -> ReportController: GET /report/export?type=pdf
    ReportController -> ReportController: Generate PDF View
    ReportController --> Administrator: Download PDF File
else Pilih Export? (Excel)
    Administrator -> View: Klik Export Excel
    View -> ReportController: GET /report/export?type=excel
    ReportController -> ReportController: Generate Spreadsheet
    ReportController --> Administrator: Download Excel File
else Hanya Tampilan Layar
    ReportController --> View: return view('report', data)
    View --> Administrator: Tampilkan Data Rekap Platform di Layar
end
@enduml